Here's a PlantUML sequence diagram representing the data flow in the MunchOut application:

```plantuml
@startuml dylanvanh_MunchOut

actor User
participant "Flutter UI" as UI
participant "BLoC" as BLOC
participant "Repository" as REPO
participant "Flask API" as API
database "Database" as DB

User -> UI: Interacts with app
UI -> BLOC: Triggers event
BLOC -> REPO: Requests data
REPO -> API: Makes API call
API -> DB: Queries database
DB --> API: Returns data
API --> REPO: Returns API response
REPO --> BLOC: Returns processed data
BLOC --> UI: Updates state
UI --> User: Displays updated information

@enduml
```